Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:55.66,INJP02,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5\fad(300,300)\pos(1895,25)}Future is lonely as it seems to be and I am reaching from there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:09.84,INJP02,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5\fad(300,300)\pos(1895,25)}My mind is clear now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:15.56,INJP02,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5\fad(300,300)\pos(1895,25)}I feel like I can do anything when I want to do it, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:19.69,INJP02,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5\fad(300,300)\pos(1895,25)}I feel I'm notorious
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:23.07,INJP02,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5\fad(300,300)\pos(1895,25)}Do you know what you can handle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:25.28,INJP02,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5\fad(300,300)\pos(1895,25)}Do you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:29.03,INJP02,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5\fad(300,300)\pos(1895,25)}Spinning round and round, going back and forth
