Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:38.21,INJP02,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5\fad(300,300)\pos(1895,25)}never end forever
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:42.38,INJP02,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5\fad(300,300)\pos(1895,25)}Out on the rim no need to breathe ever I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:45.46,INJP02,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5\fad(300,300)\pos(1895,25)}...think of my sins
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:50.26,INJP02,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5\fad(300,300)\pos(1895,25)}Forgiveness came to this fake world where I was dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:50.45,INCHT02,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5\fad(300,300)\pos(25,1055)}來吧 現在就沉浸到那忘卻的深淵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:55.66,INCHT02,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5\fad(300,300)\pos(25,1055)}孤身一人地向著那寂寞的未來前進
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:09.84,INCHT02,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5\fad(300,300)\pos(25,1055)}我現在心靈相當清澈
